strings.Value: "I don't worry about beasts. I will run away while they eat all of you."
"Nok-Nok is sly, Nok-Nok is fast. Nok-Nok will flee if beast attacks!"
"At least you don't try to pretend that you value our lives."
"I promise you won't get too far! Just try and you'll get a lightning bolt in your hind!"
"We'll manage. Then I will track you."
"Perfect! The farther the better for all of us!"
